        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Credit Reporting Accuracy After a Legal Name Change Act of 2022 </strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits, upon a consumer's request, a credit reporting agency from including on a consumer credit report a consumer's prior name after a legal name change. </p>]]>
        </text>
